              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card">
              <div class="review-image">
                <img src="images/saving.png" alt="Saving Private Ryan">
              </div>
              <div class="review-content">
                <h3>Saving Private Ryan</h3>
                <div class="review-rating">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Saving Private Ryan is a 1998 American epic war film directed by Steven Spielberg. It follows the Normandy landings and subsequent American soldiers' mission to find and bring home a paratrooper, the last surviving brother of four, amidst the chaos of World War II. The film is renowned for its graphic and realistic portrayal of war, particularly the harrowing first 30 minutes depicting the Omaha Beach assault during the Normandy landings.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
